transcript.text: So at On Pin Show we have designed 3 specialized HTML file designer studios to simplify the designing experience for your end customers.
We also offer 7000 plus complimentary templates and you can also create your own template library for your customers to design online.
So for each product you can design variety of templates and your customers are able to design by HTML File Designer studio.
So Designer studio #1 is an advanced studio which allows you to offer commercial wide format apparel, promotional invitations, label products online.
It is also configurable per product differently.
So whether you are offering a business card Oregon, a pull up banner or a white format.
It also supports a custom size designing products like apparels, T-shirts, mug, promotional items.
You can also configure the designer studio differently where you can limit the number of options, the number of colors depending on your product strategy.
You can also put an actual product images so customers are getting real to near preview when they are personalizing online.
It also generates an online preview for customers to proof online like PDF, JPG, even surface web previews for products like merks or any promotional items you are offering.

It also has an integration with the social media images so customers can use their personal images, upload the personal images, even upload the images from the Facebook, Instagram, even the stock images library like Deposit Photos, Photolia or a Pixabe.
The second specially designed studio is a photo calendar studio which is specially designed to simplify online personal agent for your own customers.
For products like custom calendars, event Diaries on each page they are able to personalize their images even they can add the custom events and it has an easy drag and drop options.
So they can personalize each and every page personalizing and putting their own images.
This is a custom calendar so they can also select the custom start month and end month and accordingly they can update the calendar pages.
And it also allows them to put their personal events so they can select a particular date box and they can add their own personal events like birthdays or anniversary.
It also helps them to apply the cliparts, backgrounds, even the common public events like US holidays, Christian holidays, Canadian holidays.
So according to your strategy, you can put your custom events and customers are able to design custom 12 pages calendar.

And the third studio what we have specially designed is a photo book studio to offer online personalization for multi page photo books here and customers can upload their images and they can also easily design the multi pages photo book.
It has a specialized tools like an autofill so they can upload number of pictures and it can auto fill onto each of the pages.
There is easy drag and drop features so any image they would like to replace they can simply drag and drop.
They also get lot of advanced image effects, borders, flip sat backgrounds.
Also each and every page they are able to personalize on their own.
There are also specialized tools like layouts.

So if they want to change the layout and have multiple images onto it automatically they can easily drag and drop and that particular pages would have number of placeholders according to the layouts they have selected in the photo book.
We also generate a flip book preview so your customers once design is over they can also generate the complete flip book preview for the photo book they have designed online.
So before completing an order they can preview it using this flip book preview available in photo book designer studio.
So these three studios which are specially designed simplifies online designing for your end customers and you can offer wide range of products online.
